Maybe a miracle will happen<br />
And this wonder can only be love<br />
But when there won&#8217;t be a miracle, I will stay alone</p>
<p>Sometimes the days are so senseless and so gloomy<br />
But I&#8217;m trusting in love and I won&#8217;t give up</p>
<p>Maybe a miracle will happen<br />
And this wonder can only be love<br />
But when there won&#8217;t be a miracle, I will stay alone</p>
<p><font color="#C0C0C0"><em>Darling, you have made this a wonderful world for me<br />
